CatDescriptText: The sign above the doorway reads, "Please Pay When Served" and the man in the two-toned shoes has a pinky ring on.  There are photographs on the walls.
TitMainTitle: Two men, one with arm around a woman wearing a polka dot dress, and one wearing eyeglasses, two toned shoes, and bow-tie, with woman in houndstooth suit seated beside them, in "Rose Room" of bar
